{"tid":510087,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「盲婆」驚世預言逐一應驗 明年中國成超級大國","createTime":"2017-12-26T06:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T07:22:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6018ee3e6be8978090e673c1647a826cf2c4db2","tid":510087,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171226/20255793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F20255793&d=ehFJHGs3Y%2BYW5K%2FkmhX8PBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=58c0dcc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F20255793&h=06d5b25e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171226/20255793</a><br />\n<br />\n「盲婆」驚世預言逐一應驗<br />\n明年中國成超級大國<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保加利亞已故失明女預言家萬加（Baba Vanga），預測來年會出現兩件可改變世界的大事。<br />\n<br />\n萬加雖然1996年以85歲高齡逝世，但她遺下的預言「錦囊」，一直預測到第51世紀世界末日為止，曾準確預測美國911恐怖襲擊、南亞海嘯、英國脫歐等。<br />\n<br />\n萬加對來年的兩大預言，包括中國取代美國成為超級大國，以及在金星發現全新能源。<br />\n<br />\n中國成為「強國」，現在看來不算甚麼大秘密，但若死了21年的萬加真的在生前已料事如神，那又是另一回事。<br />\n<br />\n說到金星，雖然目前未有探索金星的計劃，但美國太空總署（NASA）本年6月宣佈，明年將發射最新的「帕克太陽探測器」（Parker Solar Probe），史無前例飛入太陽大氣層，其間探測器將繞行距太陽第二近的金星7次，利用金星的引力減慢速度，逐步移近太陽，預計2024年12月進入太陽軌道。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》"},{"pid":"ef2f74dccc3f32e96f8adc07b8e6af79dfe989a0","tid":510087,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:07:44.000Z","msg":"預言呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7912aa08f6e93ab1560e2235af99232285c4ebb9","tid":510087,"uid":157535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:12:35.000Z","msg":"預測到51世紀未咁撚勁&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5596b5ef11052185c3549e33dd